                                <div class="pb-20">
                                    <div>How to Use:</div>
                                    <div class="d-flex pt-10">
                                        <div class="pt-5"><img
                                                src="https://qureskincaredns.com/sections/isolated/faucet-creative-brief/images/Number1.svg" alt="Number1">
                                        </div>
                                        <p class="pl-10">Clean and dry your neck and décolletage to ensure the area is
                                            clear from any dirt, sweat, or skincare products.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="d-flex pt-10">
                                        <div class="pt-5"><img
                                                src="https://qureskincaredns.com/sections/isolated/faucet-creative-brief/images/Number2.svg" alt="Number2">
                                        </div>
                                        <p class="pl-10">Insert the USB-C cable from the Neck & Décolletage LED System
                                            into the port located on the top of the controller.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="d-flex pt-10">
                                        <div class="pt-5"><img
                                                src="https://qureskincaredns.com/sections/isolated/faucet-creative-brief/images/Number_3.svg"
                                                alt="Number_3"></div>
                                        <p class="pl-10">Secure the device around the neck to comfortably treat the
                                            entire neck and décolletage area. Alternatively, position the strap across
                                            the shoulders to lower the LED panel slightly and extend coverage further
                                            across the décolletage.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="d-flex pt-10">
                                        <div class="pt-5"><img
                                                src="https://qureskincaredns.com/sections/isolated/faucet-creative-brief/images/Number_4.svg"
                                                alt="Number_4"></div>
                                        <p class="pl-10">Press the ON/OFF button on the controller. The treatment will
                                            automatically run for 10 minutes and shut off at the end of the session.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
